# Vercel Deployment Optimization
# ⚠️ CRITICAL: Exclude files that Vercel might interpret as Serverless Functions

# === Serverless Function 誤認識を防ぐファイル除外 ===
# Development scripts (Vercel が Functions として誤認識)
# --- scripts ディレクトリ ---
# 1) まずディレクトリ自体を包含
!scripts/
# 2) ディレクトリ内はデフォルトで除外
scripts/**
# 3) ビルドに必要なファイルだけ再包含
!scripts/validate_env.mjs
test-*.js
test-*.html
tmp.js

# Configuration files (ランタイム不要)
postcss.config.js
tailwind.config.js
webpack.config.js
vite.config.ts
!vite.config.ts
!tsconfig.node.json
jest.config.js
vitest.config.ts

# Testing files (Functions ではない)
**/tests/
**/__tests__/
*.test.js
*.test.ts
*.test.tsx
*.test.mjs

# === 通常の除外ファイル ===
# Development files
server/
*.md
*.txt
*.log

# Documentation
docs/
CHANGELOG.md
TROUBLESHOOTING.md
*_REPORT.md
*_GUIDE.md
*_CHECKLIST.md
architecture-alternatives.md
mongodb-atlas-setup.md
mongodb_setup.md
backend.log

# Utilities
check-db.mongo
cookies.txt
debug-checklist.md

# Environment and config files
.env*
env.example
start-with-mock.bat

# Build artifacts (handled by Vercel)
dist/
.cache/

# IDE and editor files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Vercel specific
vercel-optimized.json
vercel_logs.txt 